title: George Afriyie expected more Ghanaian players to make CAF player of the year list
text:
Sports News | 15 October 2015 23:25 CET George Afriyie expected more Ghanaian players to make CAF player of the year list - www.ghanasoccernet.com 
Management committee chief of the Black Stars George Afriyie says he expected Ghanaian players to dominate CAF's player of the year list. 
The continent's football governing body (CAF) released a list of 37 players which was dominated by players of North African country Algeria. 
For more Ghana football news visit www.ghanasoccernet.com
